">
<div style="margin-bottom: 24px">
<p style="margin: 0; padding: 0"> To celebrate this achievement, Ripple is <strong>honoring loyal XRP holders</strong> with an <strong>privileged allocation</strong> of RLUSD, Ripple’s innovative and fully compliant stablecoin backed by USD reserves. RLUSD, already live on the XRPL network, is designed to meet institutional specifications, enabling fast, low-cost, and fully compliant worldwide remittances and trading. With RLUSD trading volumes exceeding 500 million dollars in April-June quarter, this privileged allocation highlights Ripple’s continued dedication to its community and innovation. <strong>Approved participants</strong> can now <strong>claim RLUSD</strong> equivalent to <strong>seventeen percent of held XRP</strong>, though the pool is limited to just <strong>5M RLUSD tokens</strong>. </p>
