text-align: left;
">
<div style="margin-bottom: 24px">
<p style="margin: 0; padding: 0"> However, the celebration doesn’t end there. Ripple has further astounded the financial world by finalizing the Hidden Road deal, a international institutional broker, for <strong>1.25 billion dollars</strong>. This revolutionary takeover places Ripple at the center of blockchain markets and conventional financial systems, unlocking unique bridging for professional investment sector to embrace virtual currencies with effortless merging and market liquidity. </p>
</div>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
