font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif;
text-align: left;
">
<div style="margin-bottom: 24px">
<p style="margin: 0; padding: 0"> In addition to this massive purchase, Ripple’s infrastructure on the ledger continues to scale swiftly with the launch of several worldwide fiat-supported digital currencies, including <strong>USDC, XSGD, EURØP, and USDB</strong>. These stablecoins, dollar-for-dollar backed and governed by rigorous regulatory requirements, substantially improve XRPL’s utility and market liquidity. Each stablecoin tailored to regional needs, empowering effortless cross-border transactions and facilitating next-generation financial services for programmers and corporations. </p>
</div>
</td>
</tr>
